{"tid":1148930,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"住緊木屋 懷疑有好大個蜂巢係d木板中間","createTime":"2019-05-10T19:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T14:31:21.000Z","uid":171273,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f342b770e70ba697db63859e0c7e08799bb1512","tid":1148930,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的 係外國住緊<br />\n間睡房有一邊牆係木牆<br />\n木牆係空心<br />\n<br />\n中間係果d喉/線之類<br />\n<br />\n之前搬入黎發現牆身有個窿成日有蜜蜂飛入屋 果個位本身係暖氣條喉會駁埋出室外但係拆左所以有個3cm x3cm既窿係到<br />\n之後我搵野封實左就無再有蜜蜂<br />\n<br />\n但係呢排成日聽到木牆果邊成日有蜜蜂d嗡嗡聲<br />\n再有d撞落木板既聲(應該係蜜蜂撞到/蜜蜂d腳爬既聲)<br />\n<br />\n但係室外都唔點覺有蜜蜂<br />\n我懷疑木果塊牆空心果個位住左好大竇蜜蜂 但係又唔知實際位置可以點搞 雖然除左d聲幾核突都無乜影響到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b0dbc587e286cc007a776483f764715238a07d","tid":1148930,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"99bf3c2a5cbefe39be449f6f83b34bd70da9851c","tid":1148930,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"32b0dbc587e286cc007a776483f764715238a07d","tid":1148930,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:31:32.000Z","msg":"??"},{"pid":"36f53568d069cb4d0581dcc6856f4f086426069a","tid":1148930,"uid":136662,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:33:38.000Z","msg":"上網訂定十箱律路水炮啦"},{"pid":"683aaa23efb6539d73d2ab126dda8708d651398e","tid":1148930,"uid":158899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99bf3c2a5cbefe39be449f6f83b34bd70da9851c","tid":1148930,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"32b0dbc587e286cc007a776483f764715238a07d","tid":1148930,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:31:32.000Z","msg":"??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T19:34:12.000Z","msg":"圖呢  又要倒數叫伯母？<br 